11:57.542 --> 11:58.848
but we just have to be --It's not even that.

11:58.892 --> 12:00.937
It's that we have
to wait at all.

12:00.981 --> 12:03.374
It's that we are
constantly waiting

12:03.418 --> 12:06.334
just to see
if we can move forward.

12:06.377 --> 12:09.467
We were just talking about maybe
having a kid in a few years,

12:09.511 --> 12:14.124
and yet here we are, once again,
holding our breath.

12:14.168 --> 12:16.779
We just got back
to being us.

12:18.738 --> 12:20.435
[ Softly ]
I just want...

12:20.478 --> 12:21.828
I just want to be us.

12:21.871 --> 12:23.786
We are us.
We're still us.

12:23.830 --> 12:25.745
