No, but you can

13:55.008 --> 13:56.792
bring your wet meat hands
over here.

13:56.836 --> 13:57.924
Maybe we can just --

13:57.967 --> 14:00.361
[ Doorbell rings ]

14:00.404 --> 14:02.232
Alright.
Alright.

14:02.276 --> 14:03.886
But everybody's
out of here by 11:00,

14:03.930 --> 14:04.974
or we make them watch.

14:05.018 --> 14:07.324
[ Both laugh ]

14:07.368 --> 14:09.196
[ Indistinct conversations ]

14:09.239 --> 14:10.414
[ Exhales slowly ]

14:10.458 --> 14:13.026
Hey.
