14:22.862 --> 14:25.081
Yes.
Modesty is my best quality.

14:25.125 --> 14:26.300
[ Door opens ]

14:26.343 --> 14:28.345
Katherine!
I am so glad you're here.

14:28.389 --> 14:30.913
I can't wait to meet
your mystery...

14:30.957 --> 14:31.914
Hello.

14:31.958 --> 14:33.960
Ta-da!
[ Laughs ]

14:34.003 --> 14:36.266
[ Chuckles ]
You have amazing hair.

14:36.310 --> 14:39.617
