It's really nice to meet you.

14:43.883 --> 14:45.449
Come in.

14:45.493 --> 14:47.190
[ Timer beeps ]Well, it's a pomade
and then a mousse,

14:47.234 --> 14:48.888
and then you're gonna have
to hairspray it.

14:48.931 --> 14:50.106
-Oh, wow.
-Light texturizing powder.

14:50.150 --> 14:51.455
Rome: Gina, one of
the timers is going off,

14:51.499 --> 14:53.457
