15:05.948 --> 15:06.906
I'm Rome.

15:06.949 --> 15:07.907
Greta.

15:07.950 --> 15:09.952
Great name,
great hair.

15:09.996 --> 15:11.084
Right?

15:11.127 --> 15:12.172
Can I get you
a drink?

15:12.215 --> 15:13.913
Yes, that.

15:13.956 --> 15:14.914
Oh, now we know
it's not poison.

15:14.957 --> 15:15.915
Doyou?

15:15.958 --> 15:18.482
[ Rome and Katherine chuckle ]

15:18.526 --> 15:21.181
So, what's new?

15:21.224 --> 15:23.923
Uh...oh, nothing,
just got a new blouse...Oh.

