[ Doorbell rings ]

16:33.731 --> 16:35.516
Oh, that must be
Maggie and Gary.

16:35.559 --> 16:36.430
They're still coming?

16:36.473 --> 16:38.214
Uh, yeah.

16:38.258 --> 16:41.087
I gave them an out, but Maggie
said Gary wants the distraction.

16:41.130 --> 16:43.132
So please don't
mention anything tonight.

16:43.176 --> 16:45.004
Yeah, Maggie says Gary just
wants it to be a normal night,

16:45.047 --> 16:46.701
so just play it cool --[ Door shuts ]

16:46.744 --> 16:48.398
Hey!
[ Claps hands ]

16:48.442 --> 16:51.880
Hey! It's the man of the hour
right there.

16:51.923 --> 16:53.795
