I give myself a mental note

17:06.373 --> 17:08.940
to tell you how dope you look
in that coat.

17:08.984 --> 17:10.377
Dope coat.
Mm-hmm.

17:10.420 --> 17:12.422
Yeah, speaking of
dope coats...

17:12.466 --> 17:13.641
[ Laughter ]

17:13.684 --> 17:15.599
...you left this
at my party.

17:15.643 --> 17:18.776
Oh, right.
