17:18.820 --> 17:20.343
We totally made out
on that coat.

17:20.387 --> 17:23.433
[ Both laugh ]

17:23.477 --> 17:25.131
Katherine?

17:26.610 --> 17:28.351
This is Greta.

17:28.395 --> 17:31.093
She's...with me.

17:31.137 --> 17:33.226
Well, hello, plus one.

17:33.269 --> 17:35.097
I don't know if this
