18:10.350 --> 18:13.309
Yeah, especially since
all the adults are gone.

18:13.353 --> 18:14.310
Where are they?

18:14.354 --> 18:15.920
Game night
at Rome and Gina's.

18:15.964 --> 18:18.532
Oh, wait, does that mean
everything's okay with Gary?

18:20.360 --> 18:22.449
Actually,
we don't know yet.

18:22.492 --> 18:24.233
We're st-still waiting
on the results.

18:24.277 --> 18:28.019
♪♪

18:28.063 --> 18:29.717
