for what happened,

20:20.828 --> 20:22.221
so it doesn't matter
what Dad thinks.

20:22.264 --> 20:24.048
It does to me.

20:24.092 --> 20:26.616
♪♪

20:26.660 --> 20:30.141
Mom,
it wasn't your fault.

20:30.185 --> 20:32.318
[ Sniffles ]

20:32.361 --> 20:35.190
